    %% External flows
    Client -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS Edge/Reencrypt<br/>Optional client cert"| Route
    Route -->|"HTTP(S)/8080-8443<br/>Plaintext or TLS"| PredictorSvc

    %% Controller egress
    Manager -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA Token"| K8sAPI
    Manager -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>NGC API Key"| NIMAPI
    Manager -->|"HTTPS/HTTP<br/>TLS optional<br/>Bearer Token"| ModelReg

    %% Internal flows
    K8sAPI -->|"HTTPS/443→9443<br/>TLS (service-ca)"| WebhookSvc
    Prometheus -->|"HTTP/{prom-port}<br/>ServiceMonitor/PodMonitor"| ISVCMetrics

    %% Dashboard flow
    Dashboard["RHOAI Dashboard"] -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token"| GWServer
    GWServer -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>User's Bearer Token<br/>SSAR check"| K8sAPI

    %% Auth policy flow
    Manager -.->|"Creates AuthPolicy<br/>& EnvoyFilter"| AuthStack

